COMMON cb_os, platform, screen, dirsep
;  The following variables are initially set in phenot_p0:
;     - platform {string}: The current underlying OS platform; its
;       value is either 'Windows' or 'UNIX'.
;     - screen {string}: The screen device; its value is 'Win' under
;       Windows and 'X' under UNIX.
;     - dirsep {string}: The directory separator; its value is '\'
;       under Windows and '/' under Unix.